# ── Single Cloudflare Pages project · 4 sites in one deploy ───────────────────
# One project (digimax) serves all four DSM webs because the Cloudflare account
# is at its 100/100 Pages-project cap — see CONSOLIDATION.md. Each site is a
# self-contained bundle under its own path; real files serve directly, and each
# path gets its own SPA fallback so client-side routing works per-site.

# Admin SPA (built from admin-app/ under /admin) — must come BEFORE the store fallback.
/admin/*              /admin/index.html                200

# Marketing & services microsites (standalone static pages, fast load).
/marketing            /marketing/index.html            302
/services             /services/dsmAIFinal.html        302

# SPA fallback for the React store / landing (every other client route).
/*                    /index.html                      200
